#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:1
msgid "Environment Variables"
msgstr "环境变量"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:3
msgid ""
"Below are some environment variables that can be set, along with their "
"descriptions."
msgstr "以下是一些可以设置的环境变量及其说明。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:6
msgid ""
"Since MagiAttention is actively evolving, many advanced but experimental "
"features will be released but enabled through environment variables."
msgstr "由于 MagiAttention 正在积极发展中，许多高级但实验性的功能将通过环境变量启用后发布。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:14
msgid "For Correctness"
msgstr "正确性相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:16
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:18
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable high-precision (fp32) reduce for "
"partial out during dist-attn forward to trade-off double comm overhead for "
"increased precision and less dtype-cast overhead. The default value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 dist-attn 前向传播中 partial out "
"的高精度（fp32）reduce，以双倍通信开销换取更高精度和更少的 dtype 转换开销。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:22
msgid ""
"Inside the ffa forward kernel, we always use high-precision (fp32) "
"accumulation for partial out."
msgstr "在 ffa 前向内核内部，我们始终对 partial out 使用高精度（fp32）累加。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:24
msgid "We always use high-precision (fp32) lse everywhere."
msgstr "我们在所有地方始终使用高精度（fp32）的 lse。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:26
msgid "This feature works for out only when enabling qo comm."
msgstr "此功能仅在启用 qo comm 时对 out 生效。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:30
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BACKWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BACKWARD_HIGH_PRECISION_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:32
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable high-precision (fp32) reduce for "
"partial dq,dk,dv during dist-attn backward to trade-off double comm overhead"
" for increased precision and less dtype-cast overhead. The default value is "
"`0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 dist-attn 反向传播中 partial dq,dk,dv "
"的高精度（fp32）reduce，以双倍通信开销换取更高精度和更少的 dtype 转换开销。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:36
msgid ""
"Inside the ffa backward kernel, we always use high-precision (fp32) "
"accumulation for partial dq,dk,dv."
msgstr "在 ffa 反向内核内部，我们始终对 partial dq,dk,dv 使用高精度（fp32）累加。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:38
msgid "This feature works for dq only when enabling qo comm."
msgstr "此功能仅在启用 qo comm 时对 dq 生效。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:42
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DSINK_ALL_REDUCE_OP**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:44
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the all-reduce op for sink "
"gradients within `dist_attn_func` when involving attention sink. The default"
" value is `none`. And options are within {`none`, `sum`, `avg`}."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量的值以控制涉及 attention sink 时 `dist_attn_func` 中 sink 梯度的 all-reduce "
"操作。默认值为 `none`。可选值为 {`none`、`sum`、`avg`}。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:48
msgid ""
"For now we only accept global replicated sink tensor as input to feed into "
"`dist_attn_func`, and the gradients of sink in each cp rank are partial and "
"requires to be sum-reduced across cp ranks."
msgstr ""
"目前我们仅接受全局复制的 sink 张量作为输入传入 `dist_attn_func`，每个 cp rank 中的 sink 梯度是部分的，需要在 cp"
" rank 之间进行 sum-reduce。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:50
msgid ""
"However, since sink tensor is learnable, it will be considered as a regular "
"parameter in the model similar to `bias` in `nn.Linear` layer."
msgstr "然而，由于 sink 张量是可学习的，它将被视为模型中的常规参数，类似于 `nn.Linear` 层中的 `bias`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:52
msgid ""
"So under some popular training frameworks, such as Megatron-LM, FSDP, the "
"sum-reduction across cp ranks of the partial gradients of sink might be "
"automatically applied within the whole `dp x cp` mesh."
msgstr ""
"因此在一些流行的训练框架（如 Megatron-LM、FSDP）中，sink 部分梯度在 cp rank 之间的 sum-reduction "
"可能会在整个 `dp x cp` mesh 中自动执行。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:54
msgid ""
"To avoid repeated reduction, we provide this environment variable to specify"
" the all-reduce op for sink gradients within `dist_attn_func`, whose default"
" value is `none` to NOT apply any reduction to sink gradients by "
"`dist_attn_func` and let the framework handle it."
msgstr ""
"为避免重复 reduction，我们提供此环境变量来指定 `dist_attn_func` 中 sink 梯度的 all-reduce 操作，其默认值为"
" `none`，即 `dist_attn_func` 不对 sink 梯度执行任何 reduction，而由框架来处理。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:56
msgid ""
"However, under the scenarios w/o any framework mechanism to reduce "
"parameters across cp ranks, you have to specify this environment variable to"
" `sum`."
msgstr "但在没有任何框架机制来跨 cp rank reduce 参数的场景下，您必须将此环境变量设为 `sum`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:58
msgid ""
"And sometimes, `avg` might also be an option when you need to scale the sink"
" gradients by `1/cp`."
msgstr "有时 `avg` 也是一个选项，当您需要将 sink 梯度按 `1/cp` 缩放时可以使用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:62
msgid "For Performance"
msgstr "性能相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:64
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FA4_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:66
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to ``1`` to switch the attn kernel backend from "
"`FFA` to `FFA_FA4`, a monkey patch version of Flash-Attention 4, to "
"temporarily support arbitrary mask on Blackwell GPUs. The default value is "
"`0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以将注意力内核后端从 `FFA` 切换到 `FFA_FA4`——Flash-Attention 4 的 monkey "
"patch 版本，以临时支持 Blackwell GPU 上的任意掩码。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:69
msgid ""
"This is for now a workaround solution might be removed or updated in the "
"future."
msgstr "这目前是一个临时解决方案，未来可能会被移除或更新。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:72
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NATIVE_GRPCOLL**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NATIVE_GRPCOLL**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:74
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable native kernel implementation for "
"group collective comm. The default value is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 group collective 通信的原生内核实现。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:77
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:86
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:95
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now, and not "
"compatible with many other features, thus please do NOT enable it unless you"
" know exactly what you are doing."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中，与许多其他功能不兼容，因此请不要启用，除非您清楚了解其影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:81
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_QO_COMM**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_QO_COMM**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:83
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable query/output communication, "
"including fetching remote q (fwd), reducing partial out and lse (fwd), "
"fetching remote q,o,lse,do (bwd), reducing partial dq (bwd), to eliminate "
"the restriction that communication is limited solely to key/value. The "
"default value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 query/output 通信，包括获取远程 q（前向）、reduce partial out 和 "
"lse（前向）、获取远程 q,o,lse,do（反向）、reduce partial dq（反向），以消除通信仅限于 key/value "
"的限制。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:90
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FLATTEN_HEAD_GROUPS**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FLATTEN_HEAD_GROUPS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:92
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to ``1`` to flatten head groups within GQA/MQA "
"attention to optimize dynamic solver performance. The default value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以展平 GQA/MQA attention 中的 head groups 来优化 dynamic solver "
"性能。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:99
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_AUTO_RANGE_MERGE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_AUTO_RANGE_MERGE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:101
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to ``1`` to enable automatic range merging for "
"flex-flash-attention, to improve performance by reducing the number of "
"attention ranges. The default value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以启用 flex-flash-attention 的自动范围合并，通过减少注意力范围的数量来提升性能。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:105
#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:114
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now, thus "
"please do NOT enable it unless you know exactly what you are doing."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中，因此请不要启用，除非您清楚了解其影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:109
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CATGQA**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CATGQA**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:111
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to ``1`` to enable CatGQA mode for flex-flash-"
"attention backward, to further optimize the performance under GQA settings "
"by concatenating multiple Q heads sharing the same KV head. The default "
"value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以启用 flex-flash-attention 反向的 CatGQA 模式，通过拼接共享相同 KV head 的多个 Q"
" head 来进一步优化 GQA 设置下的性能。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:118
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BWD_HIDE_TAIL_REDUCE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BWD_HIDE_TAIL_REDUCE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:120
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to ``1`` to trade saving the last remote `kv` "
"activation for reordering overlap stages during backward, hiding the final "
"remote `group_reduce` with the host FFA stage. The default value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 ``1`` 以牺牲保存最后一个远程 `kv` 激活来重排反向传播中的重叠阶段，将最终的远程 `group_reduce` 隐藏在主机 "
"FFA 阶段中。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:123
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now, and not "
"compatible with many other features like qo comm, thus please do NOT enable "
"it unless you know exactly what you are doing."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中，与许多其他功能（如 qo comm）不兼容，因此请不要启用，除非您清楚了解其影响。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:127
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FORWARD_SM_MARGIN**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FORWARD_SM_MARGIN**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:129
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of SMs of the ffa "
"forward kernel saved for comm kernels. The default value is `4` if "
"`CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS` > `1`, otherwise `0`."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量的值以控制 ffa 前向内核为通信内核预留的 SM 数量。当 `CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS` > `1` "
"时默认值为 `4`，否则为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:131
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_BACKWARD_SM_MARGIN**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_BACKWARD_SM_MARGIN**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:133
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of SMs of the ffa "
"backward kernel saved for comm kernels. The default value is `4` if "
"`CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS` > `1`, otherwise `0`."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量的值以控制 ffa 反向内核为通信内核预留的 SM 数量。当 `CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS` > `1` "
"时默认值为 `4`，否则为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:135
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CPP_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_CPP_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:137
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable C++ backend for core data "
"structures (`AttnRange`, `AttnMaskType`, etc.) to avoid Python overhead. The"
" default value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用核心数据结构（`AttnRange`、`AttnMaskType` 等）的 C++ 后端，以避免 Python "
"开销。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:140
msgid ""
"This feature is experimental and under active development for now. If the "
"C++ extension is not found or this variable is set to `0`, it will fall back"
" to the Python implementation."
msgstr "此功能目前处于实验阶段并在积极开发中。如果未找到 C++ 扩展或此变量设为 `0`，将回退到 Python 实现。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:144
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_HIERARCHICAL_COMM**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_HIERARCHICAL_COMM**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:146
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable hierarchical group-collective comm"
" within 2-dim cp group (inter_node group + intra_node group). The default "
"value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用二维 cp group（inter_node group + intra_node group）内的分层 group-"
"collective 通信。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:149
msgid ""
"This is for now a temporary solution to reduce the redundant inter-node "
"communication and might be removed or updated in the future."
msgstr "这目前是减少冗余节点间通信的临时方案，未来可能会被移除或更新。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:152
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DIST_ATTN_RUNTIME_DICT_SIZE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DIST_ATTN_RUNTIME_DICT_SIZE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:154
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the maximum LRU cache size of "
"`dist_attn_runtime_dict_mgr`. The default value is `1000`."
msgstr "设置此环境变量的值以控制 `dist_attn_runtime_dict_mgr` 的最大 LRU 缓存大小。默认值为 `1000`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:156
msgid "**CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS**"
msgstr "**CUDA_DEVICE_MAX_CONNECTIONS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:158
msgid ""
"This environment variable defines the number of hardware queues that CUDA "
"streams can utilize. Increasing this value can improve the overlap of "
"communication and computation, but may also increase PCIe traffic. The "
"default value is `8`."
msgstr ""
"此环境变量定义了 CUDA stream 可以使用的硬件队列数量。增大此值可以改善通信与计算的重叠，但也可能增加 PCIe 流量。默认值为 `8`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:161
msgid "For Debug"
msgstr "调试相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:163
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SANITY_CHECK**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SANITY_CHECK**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:165
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable many sanity check codes inside "
"magi_attention. The default value is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 magi_attention 内部的大量健全性检查代码。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:168
msgid ""
"This is only supposed to be used for testing or debugging, since the extra "
"sanity-check overhead might be non-negligible."
msgstr "此功能仅用于测试或调试，因为额外的健全性检查开销可能不容忽视。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:171
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SDPA_BACKEND**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:173
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` can switch the attn kernel backend from ffa "
"to sdpa-math, to support higher precision like `fp32` or `fp64`. The default"
" value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 可将注意力内核后端从 ffa 切换到 sdpa-math，以支持更高精度（如 `fp32` 或 `fp64`）。默认值为 "
"`0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:176
msgid ""
"This is only supposed to be used for testing or debugging, since the "
"performance is not acceptable."
msgstr "此功能仅用于测试或调试，因为其性能不可接受。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:179
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DETERMINISTIC_MODE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_DETERMINISTIC_MODE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:181
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable deterministic mode to use "
"deterministic algorithms for all magi_attention kernels. The default value "
"is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用确定性模式，对所有 magi_attention 内核使用确定性算法。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:184
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PROFILE_MODE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PROFILE_MODE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:186
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable profiling mode to profile all "
"magi_attention kernels, currently mainly for ffa kernels (*see "
"[here](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/exps/attn/profile_ffa) for more details*). The "
"default value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用性能分析模式，对所有 magi_attention 内核进行性能分析，目前主要针对 ffa "
"内核（*详情请参阅[此处](https://github.com/SandAI-"
"org/MagiAttention/tree/main/exps/attn/profile_ffa)*）。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:189
msgid ""
"This is only supposed to be used for development. Please do NOT enable it in"
" production."
msgstr "此功能仅用于开发，请勿在生产环境中启用。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:192
msgid "For Build"
msgstr "构建相关"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:194
msgid "JIT"
msgstr "JIT"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:196
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_WORKSPACE_BASE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_WORKSPACE_BASE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:198
msgid ""
"Specifies the base directory for the MagiAttention workspace, which includes"
" cache and generated source files. If not set, it defaults to the user's "
"home directory (`~`)."
msgstr "指定 MagiAttention 工作空间的基础目录，包含缓存和生成的源文件。如果未设置，默认为用户主目录（`~`）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:200
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_VERBOSE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_VERBOSE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:202
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable verbose output during the JIT "
"compilation process, showing the full ninja build commands being executed. "
"The default value is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 JIT 编译过程中的详细输出，显示正在执行的完整 ninja 构建命令。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:204
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_DEBUG**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_DEBUG**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:206
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable debug flags for the C++/CUDA "
"compiler. This includes options like `-g` (debugging symbols) and other "
"flags to get more detailed information, such as register usage. The default "
"value is `0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用 C++/CUDA 编译器的调试标志。这包括 "
"`-g`（调试符号）等选项和其他用于获取更详细信息（如寄存器使用情况）的标志。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:209
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NO_BUILD_CACHE**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_NO_BUILD_CACHE**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:211
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to disable caching for built ffa kernels. "
"The default value is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以禁用已构建 ffa 内核的缓存。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:213
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_JIT_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FORCE_JIT_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:215
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to force building FFA in JIT mode, even the "
"pre-built AOT `libs` exists. The default value is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 以强制以 JIT 模式构建 FFA，即使预构建的 AOT `libs` 已存在。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:217
msgid "**NVCC_THREADS**"
msgstr "**NVCC_THREADS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:219
msgid ""
"Sets the number of threads for `nvcc`'s `--split-compile` option, which can "
"speed up the JIT compilation of CUDA kernels. The default value is `4`."
msgstr "设置 `nvcc` 的 `--split-compile` 选项的线程数，可加速 CUDA 内核的 JIT 编译。默认值为 `4`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:222
msgid "AOT"
msgstr "AOT"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:224
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA_JOBS**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA_JOBS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:226
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of parallel "
"compilation jobs used to pre-build ffa kernels. The default value is the "
"ceiling of `90%` of the available CPU cores (i.e. `ceil(num_cpu_cores * "
"0.9)`)."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量的值以控制预构建 ffa 内核时使用的并行编译任务数。默认值为可用 CPU 核心数的 `90%` 上取整（即 "
"`ceil(num_cpu_cores * 0.9)`）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:228
msgid "**MAX_JOBS**"
msgstr "**MAX_JOBS**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:230
msgid ""
"Set the value of this env variable to control the number of parallel "
"compilation jobs used to build the extension modules other than ffa. The "
"default value is the ceiling of `90%` of the available CPU cores (i.e. "
"`ceil(num_cpu_cores * 0.9)`)."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量的值以控制构建 ffa 以外的扩展模块时使用的并行编译任务数。默认值为可用 CPU 核心数的 `90%` 上取整（即 "
"`ceil(num_cpu_cores * 0.9)`）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:232
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_PREBUILD_FFA**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:234
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` to enable pre-build ffa kernels for some "
"common options with `ref_block_size=None` and leave others built in jit "
"mode. The default value is `1`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以启用对一些 `ref_block_size=None` 的常见选项预构建 ffa 内核，其余选项则以 JIT "
"模式构建。默认值为 `1`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:236
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_EXT_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_EXT_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:238
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` can skip building `magi_attn_ext`. The "
"default value is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 可跳过构建 `magi_attn_ext`。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:240
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_COMM_BUILD**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_SKIP_MAGI_ATTN_COMM_BUILD**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:242
msgid ""
"Toggle this env variable to `1` can skip building `magi_attn_comm`. The "
"default value is `0`."
msgstr "将此环境变量设为 `1` 可跳过构建 `magi_attn_comm`。默认值为 `0`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:244
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_FFA_FA4_CACHE_DIR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:246
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to specify the cache directory for pre-compiled "
"`FFA_FA4` kernels. The default value is `magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/`."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以指定预编译 `FFA_FA4` 内核的缓存目录。默认值为 `magi_attention/lib/ffa_fa4_cache/`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:248
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:250
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to specify the compute capability used to build "
"MagiAttention extension modules (affects `magi_attn_comm` and "
"`create_block_mask`). Supports comma-separated values for multi-arch builds,"
" e.g. `MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY=90,100`. If not set, we will"
" try to detect the compute capability of the current GPU device. And we will"
" raise an error if detection fails."
msgstr ""
"设置此环境变量以指定构建 MagiAttention 扩展模块时使用的计算能力（影响 "
"`magi_attn_comm` 和 `create_block_mask`）。支持逗号分隔的多架构值，"
"例如 `MAGI_ATTENTION_BUILD_COMPUTE_CAPABILITY=90,100`。"
"如果未设置，我们将尝试检测当前 GPU 设备的计算能力。如果检测失败将抛出错误。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:252
msgid "**MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12**"
msgstr "**MAGI_ATTENTION_ALLOW_BUILD_WITH_CUDA12**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:254
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to `1` to allow building MagiAttention extension "
"modules with `CUDA-12`, which might cause significant performance "
"degradation compared to `CUDA-13+`. The default value is `0`, in which case "
"we will raise an error and abort the installation if the CUDA version is "
"lower than `13.0`."
msgstr ""
"将此环境变量设为 `1` 以允许使用 `CUDA-12` 构建 MagiAttention 扩展模块，这可能导致与 `CUDA-13+` "
"相比显著的性能下降。默认值为 `0`，在此情况下，如果 CUDA 版本低于 `13.0`，我们将抛出错误并中止安装。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:256
msgid "**NVSHMEM_DIR**"
msgstr "**NVSHMEM_DIR**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:258
msgid ""
"Set this env variable to the path of the custom `nvshmem` installation "
"directory."
msgstr "设置此环境变量为自定义 `nvshmem` 安装目录的路径。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:260
msgid ""
"If not set, it defaults to find the system module `nvidia-nvshmem-cu12` as "
"listed in `requirements.txt`."
msgstr "如果未设置，默认查找 `requirements.txt` 中列出的系统模块 `nvidia-nvshmem-cu12`。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/env_variables.md:262
msgid ""
"If not found anywhere, all relative features used in native group collective"
" comm kernels are disabled."
msgstr "如果在任何位置都未找到，native group collective 通信内核中的所有相关功能将被禁用。"
